<D>__{don't be, you're not doing it to me.}
<C>__{will emerson}
<D>__{i know...but i'm still sorry. at least you'll have some decent cash to walk away with.}
<C>__{seth}
<D>__{only if we can get this done, right?}
<C>__{will emerson}
<D>__{we'll get it done.}
<C>__{seth}
<D>__{how?}
