<D>__{i'm trying to figure that out right now.}
<C>__{seth}
<D>__{there aren't really enough willing buyers out there right now.}
<C>__{will emerson}
<D>__{i'm trying to think of every last one of them i can and then i will make them willing.}
<A>__{this line sits there for a minute and will looks out onto the city.}
<C>__{seth}
<D>__{are you ok with that?}
<C>__{will emerson}
<D>__{i'm about to completely fuck guys i've been doing business with for fifteen years so no i'm not exactly ok with it. but look, every last one of them would do the same thing to me in a second...so it is what it is.}
<C>__{seth}
<D>__{i guess. and what about everyone else?}
