<D>__{everyone else?}
<C>__{seth}
<D>__{normal people.}
<C>__{will emerson}
<D>__{what are you a socialist? fuck me seth.}
<A>__{will looks over at seth, sizing him up, looking to see if he has what it takes.}
<C>__{will emerson }
<D>__{look, if you want to do this with your life, and do it well, you need to believe that you are necessary. and you are. if people want to live like this...with their big cars and these houses that they haven't even paid for. then you are necessary. the only reason they can continue to live like kings is because we've got our fingers on the scale in their favor. and if i were to take my finger off...}
<C>__{will emerson }
<D>__{then the whole world gets really fucking fair, really fucking quickly. and no one wants that, they say they do...but they don't. they want what we're giving them, but they also want to play innocent and pretend they have no idea how we get it. and that's more hypocrisy than i can swallow. so fuck em.}
